{"tid":1992863,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【非洲反了】尼日利亞律師團狀告中国 求償2000億美元","createTime":"2020-04-28T11:31:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T05:33:26.000Z","uid":293677,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4c89a81de02d298dc964792457409fbb41c93218","tid":1992863,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">註：奈及利亞=尼日利亞</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">非洲第一槍！奈及利亞律師團為疫情狀告中國 求償2000億美元</span></ins><br />\n<br />\n2020-04-28 10:54:52<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕非洲第一槍！武漢肺炎造成世界諸多國家在人民生命以及經濟上的重大損失，奈及利亞有律師團決定提起訴訟，向中國求償2000億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">《Daily Sabah》報導，奈及利亞一群律師準備狀告中國，並求償2000億美元（近6兆台幣），奈及利亞律師聲明，中國應負起武漢肺炎的責任，賠償奈及利亞生命喪失、經濟受困、社會動亂、國家創傷、精神折磨以及人民日常生活的破壞，該律師團首席顧問為律師Epiphany Azinge。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，奈及利亞律師團制定兩階段計畫，首先向奈及利亞聯邦高等法院提告，接著說服奈及利亞政府在海牙國際法庭對中國提出國家訴訟，中國駐奈及利亞大使館將會收到訴訟。<br />\n<br />\n截至目前奈及利亞共1273人確診，40人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3147846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3147846&d=mbsn9%2Fi9gU9wZYjOUdyYPpriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=fa1efd8f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3147846&h=837101f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3147846</a><br />\n_____________________________________<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">中国的老朋友反目成仇了</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/20UWiZM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F20UWiZM.png&h=e8a90725&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6SEgMu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6SEgMu.jpg&h=692cc653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00ac226a35cb2ed4028d80ae1559ea620043aace","tid":1992863,"uid":236414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ridRi1O.gif\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" />"},{"pid":"e0c06983a52eb81dbdcc6bab2809a50b37035774","tid":1992863,"uid":59832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:37:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">🎩<br />\n😎⚰️</span>"},{"pid":"cc71e703b80cc813a2a41cc45806982282eb0148","tid":1992863,"uid":262674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00ac226a35cb2ed4028d80ae1559ea620043aace","tid":1992863,"uid":236414,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/ridRi1O.gif\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" /><img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/d56YkAN.gif\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T11:37:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"140d78c1be48fee492cae8beb7